resources.string: Read, read, read. Read everything -- trash, classics, good and bad, and see how they do it. Just like a carpenter who works as an apprentice and studies the master.Read! You will absorb it.Then write.If it is good, you will find out. If it is not, throw it out of the window.
मेरे गृह नगर में आपका स्वागत है
میرے آبائی شہر میں آپ کا استقبال ہے
